Eudamus had been left by Alexander as a Macedonian "resident" with Taxiles (Arrian, <I>Anabasis</I>, 6.27.2)<!--</A>ARRIAN:ANABASIS-->. We know nothing further of the attack on Porus. This Eudamus is not the brother of Pithon mentioned at the beginning of this chapter.


